---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const serviceSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "National DOOH Advertising Campaign",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Sports Digital Network"
  },
  "description": "Coast-to-coast digital out-of-home advertising campaigns across 100+ sports venues in Canada. 35M weekly impressions. Programmatic or direct buying.",
  "areaServed": {
    "@type": "Country",
    "name": "Canada"
  },
  "serviceType": "National Digital Out-of-Home Advertising"
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="National DOOH Campaigns Across Canada | Coast to Coast | SDN"
  description="Run coast-to-coast digital out-of-home campaigns in 100+ sports venues across Canada. 35M weekly impressions. Programmatic or direct. Premium demographics."
  canonicalPath="/advertisers/national/"
  schema={serviceSchema}
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Coast-to-coast reach in Canada's most engaged venues</h1>
    <p>National brands need scale, premium demographics, and brand-safe environments. SDN delivers all three through 100+ community sports venues from Vancouver to Halifax.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-highlight">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">35M</span>
          <span class="stat-label">weekly impressions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">3.6M</span>
          <span class="stat-label">weekly visitors</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">35%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">above median HHI</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">90+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">minutes dwell time</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="lead">For agencies and national media buyers, SDN offers programmatic buying through Broadsign and all major DSPs, direct deals, and private marketplace access.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why national brands add SDN to their media plans</h2>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Incremental reach that digital can't deliver</h3>
          <p>Your target audience spends time in places where mobile and desktop ads don't follow them. A parent watching their child's hockey game isn't scrolling Instagram. A golfer in the clubhouse after a round isn't checking email.</p>
          <p>SDN reaches these consumers during the 90+ minutes they're unreachable by digital — making our impressions additive to your existing digital and social campaigns, not duplicative.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <h3>Frequency through natural behaviour</h3>
          <p>Unlike transit or billboard campaigns where frequency depends on commute patterns, community venue visitors return to the same building 2-4 times per week.</p>
          <p>A 4-week campaign at a multi-pad arena can deliver 8-16 exposures per visitor — the kind of frequency that drives measurable brand lift.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="demographics-box">
        <h3>Premium audience composition</h3>
        <p>Community arenas and private golf courses attract a demographic profile that national brands pay a premium to reach elsewhere:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Household income:</strong> 35% above national average</li>
          <li><strong>Homeownership:</strong> Significantly above national rate</li>
          <li><strong>Family composition:</strong> Predominantly dual-income families with children</li>
          <li><strong>Vehicle ownership:</strong> Multiple vehicles per household is the norm</li>
          <li><strong>Financial products:</strong> Active users of banking, insurance, and investment services</li>
          <li><strong>Consumer spending:</strong> Higher than average spend in dining, travel, automotive, and retail</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="verification-box">
        <h3>Verified, fraud-free impressions</h3>
        <p>Every screen on our network is connected and monitored. Impressions are calculated from verified venue foot traffic data — not modelled estimates. Proof-of-play reporting confirms that your ad ran as scheduled. No bots. No invalid traffic. No inflated numbers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="buying-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Buying SDN inventory</h2>
      <div class="buying-grid">
        <div class="buying-card">
          <h3>Programmatic DOOH</h3>
          <p>SDN is integrated with <strong>Broadsign</strong> and available through all major demand-side platforms. Agencies can activate SDN inventory using existing DOOH buying workflows with no new contracts or manual processes required.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Open exchange</strong> — available through standard programmatic DOOH buys</li>
            <li><strong>Private marketplaces (PMP)</strong> — preferred rates and priority access via Deal IDs</li>
            <li><strong>Targeting</strong> — geography, daypart, venue type, audience segment</li>
            <li><strong>Reporting</strong> — impression delivery, proof-of-play, audience verification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="buying-card">
          <h3>Direct deals</h3>
          <p>For brands that want guaranteed placements, category exclusivity, or custom campaigns, our team manages direct buys with flexible terms and dedicated account support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="buying-card">
          <h3>Integrated campaigns</h3>
          <p>Combine digital screen placements with on-site activations — product sampling, sponsored events, tournament title sponsorship, venue branding, and grassroots community engagement. SDN's venue relationships and on-site teams make integrated campaigns turnkey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="coverage-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>National coverage</h2>
      <p>SDN operates in every major Canadian market:</p>
      <div class="coverage-table">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Region</th>
              <th>Key markets</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Ontario</strong></td>
              <td>Toronto (GTA), Ottawa, Hamilton, Kitchener-Waterloo, London, Brantford, Oshawa</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>British Columbia</strong></td>
              <td>Vancouver, Pitt Meadows</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Alberta</strong></td>
              <td>Calgary, Cochrane, Grande Prairie</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Saskatchewan</strong></td>
              <td>Regina, Saskatoon</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Atlantic Canada</strong></td>
              <td>Halifax, Moncton</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="partners-note">Our facility partners — ClubLink (24 private golf courses), Canlan Sports (private arenas), and Nustadia Recreation (community arenas) — represent the biggest and busiest venues in each market. 95% of our venues are multi-pad or multi-sport facilities.</p>
      <a href="/network/locations/" class="btn btn-secondary">See the full network map</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Creative specifications</h2>
      <div class="specs-table">
        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Resolution</strong></td>
              <td>1920 x 1080 px (16:9)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Static</strong></td>
              <td>JPG or PNG, max 5 MB</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Video</strong></td>
              <td>MP4, H.264, up to 15 seconds</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Audio</strong></td>
              <td>No audio (screens are in public spaces)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>File delivery</strong></td>
              <td>Upload to our portal or via email</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Design services</strong></td>
              <td>Available at no charge for qualifying campaigns</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>Full creative specifications and templates available in our media kit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Get started with a national campaign</h2>
    <p>Request our media kit or schedule a call with our national sales team. We'll build a custom proposal based on your campaign objectives, target markets, and budget.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/resources/media-kit/" class="btn-white">Request media kit</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-outline">Contact national sales</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .stats-highlight {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600, #495057);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .why-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .benefit-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .benefit-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .benefit-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .benefit-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .demographics-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--dark) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .demographics-box h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .demographics-box p {
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .demographics-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .demographics-box li {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .demographics-box li::before {
    content: ">";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .verification-box {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .verification-box h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .verification-box p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .buying-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .buying-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .buying-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .buying-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .buying-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .buying-card p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .buying-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .buying-card li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .coverage-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .coverage-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .coverage-section > .container > p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .coverage-table {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  th, td {
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200, #e9ecef);
  }
  th {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .partners-note {
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    color: var(--black);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--gray-200, #e9ecef);
  }

  .specs-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }
  .specs-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .specs-table {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .specs-table td:first-child {
    width: 140px;
  }
  .specs-section > .container > p {
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
